WEBVTT

1
00:40:21.670 --> 00:40:23.010 
我们开工吧 加藤
Let's get to work, Kato.

2
00:40:24.580 --> 00:40:25.930 
我们有计划了
All right, we got a plan.

3
00:40:25.940 --> 00:40:27.980 
小单子做起 逐渐做大
Start small, work our way up to the top.

4
00:40:27.980 --> 00:40:28.980 
没问题
Okay.

5
00:40:30.150 --> 00:40:31.280 
我们需要一辆车
We'll need a car.

6
00:40:31.280 --> 00:40:32.720 
废话 我们当然要用车
Hell's yes, we'll need a car.

7
00:40:32.720 --> 00:40:34.510 
内置武器
With internal weapons.

8
00:40:35.020 --> 00:40:37.470 
-装甲 -旋转的钢圈
-And armor. -Cool rims, spinning rims.

9
00:40:37.470 --> 00:40:38.700 
还要有碎冰机
Slurpee machine.

10
00:40:38.700 --> 00:40:40.270 
鸣笛也要设成墨西哥民歌
A horn that plays La Cucaracha.

11
00:40:40.270 --> 00:40:42.200 
肯定会从头到尾都棒极了
It'll be loaded up the ass with cool shit.

12
00:40:42.210 --> 00:40:45.210 
-我能办到 -加藤 我希望你与我携手
-I can do that. -Kato, I want you to take my hand.

13
00:40:45.520 --> 00:40:47.720 
我希望你能够与我一起开始冒险
And I want you to come with me on this adventure.

14
00:40:47.840 --> 00:40:49.100 
我会与你一起冒险
I'll go with you.

15
00:40:49.100 --> 00:40:51.040 
但我不要摸到你
But I don't want to touch you.

16
00:40:51.040 --> 00:40:52.340 
好 你不必拉我的手
Okay, you don't have to take my hand.

